{"arkId":"cl010113857","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113857","modified ":"2026-03-11","title":"Pot \u00e0 oille et son plateau d\u0027une paire (TH 579)","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Pot \u00e0 oille et son plateau d\u0027une paire (TH 579)"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1730","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 605 - Stavros S. Niarchos, Vitrine 11","room":"Salle 605, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1730,"endYear":"","imprecision":"vers","text":"2e quart du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Manufacture de Meissen","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q76941091"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"TH 580","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"pot \u00e0 oille","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Pot-\u00e0-oille de forme circulaire \u00e0 panse sph\u00e9rique, deux anses lat\u00e9rales, couvercle ind\u00e9pendant et bomb\u00e9, ce dernier surmont\u00e9 d\u0027un chinois agenouill\u00e9 en ronde-bosse. D\u00e9cor peint polychrome et or : sur l\u0027une des faces, d\u0027un groupe de chinois se chauffant autour d\u0027un brasero ; et sur l\u0027autre face, d\u0027un personnage chinois assis sur un fauteuil. Ces figures se dressent sur un lambrequin d\u0027or \u00e0 draperie bleue ou violette. Sur le couvercle, marli orn\u00e9 de quatre groupes de chinois \u00e9galement sur lambrequins, alternant avec des coquilles d\u0027or et des fleurons. Pi\u00e9douche bas et moulur\u00e9. Plateau circulaire \u00e0 bord droit. Marli peint en or et en couleurs de quatre m\u00e9daillons oblongs \u00e0 paysages alternant avec des rinceaux et des quadrill\u00e9s en or. Fond d\u00e9cor\u00e9 de jet\u00e9es de fleurs polychromes ; revers du marli orn\u00e9 de trois bouquets de fleurs.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; Deux \u00e9p\u00e9es entrecrois\u00e9es peintes en bleu (Sur le pot \u00e0 oille et sur le plateau)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"19","displayDimension":"19 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":5,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"22","displayDimension":"22 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":6,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"16","displayDimension":"16 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":8,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"4,5","displayDimension":"4,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":9,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"29,5","displayDimension":"29,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":12,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : porcelaine dure\r\nTechnique : techniques c\u00e9ramique","placeOfCreation":"Meissen = Mei\u00dfen (Allemagne-\u003ESaxe)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Legs \u00c9lise Dosne-Thiers, 1880, sous r\u00e9serve d\u0027usufruit de sa s\u0153ur F\u00e9licie Dosne qui y renonce et ex\u00e9cute le legs en 1881.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme Dosne-Thiers, Elise","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs sous r\u00e9serve d\u0027usufruit","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date d\u0027arriv\u00e9e au Mus\u00e9e","value":"1881","startYear":1881,"endYear":1881}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps moder